Reasoning: The paper focuses on the detection of vandalism in Wikipedia, which involves the use of machine learning and feature analysis techniques. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Computational Complexity (cs.CY), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), or Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
